title: An exciting outcome in Presidents Cup, nothing more
text:
> Top News An exciting outcome in Presidents Cup, nothing more United States' Rickie Fowler takes a selfie photo as he celebrate's after defeating the International team 15 1/2 to 14 1/2 to retain the Presidents Cup at the Jack Nicklaus Golf Club Korea, in Incheon, South Korea, Sunday, Oct. 11, 2015.(AP Photo/Woohae Cho) iWitness7 is your chance to join the News Center 7 team!
